From: =?UTF-8?q?J=C3=A9rome=20Perrin?= <jerome@nexedi.com>
Date: Tue, 24 Mar 2026 10:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Remove distutils usage for Python 3.13 compatibility

distutils was removed in Python 3.13. Use sysconfig module instead.

Reference: https://docs.python.org/3.13/whatsnew/3.13.html
---
 cmake/modules/Distutils.cmake | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/cmake/modules/Distutils.cmake b/cmake/modules/Distutils.cmake
index 8eb9e42f402..12345678901 100644
--- a/cmake/modules/Distutils.cmake
+++ b/cmake/modules/Distutils.cmake
@@ -76,7 +76,7 @@ function(distutils_add_cython_module target name src)
 
   set(suffix_var "EXT_SUFFIX")
   execute_process(COMMAND "${Python3_EXECUTABLE}" -c
-    "from distutils import sysconfig; print(sysconfig.get_config_var('${suffix_var}'))"
+    "from sysconfig import get_config_var; print(get_config_var('${suffix_var}'))"
      RESULT_VARIABLE result
      OUTPUT_VARIABLE ext_suffix
      ERROR_VARIABLE error
-- 
2.30.2